{"data":[{"id":563807451,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c230de3aa569a69b6b9195e29bd1a645","url_token":"zhu-xing-hai-37","name":"遗忘的塔纳利斯","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0077c27cb5ed8556f19c24ca43dfe696_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0077c27cb5ed8556f19c24ca43dfe696_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c230de3aa569a69b6b9195e29bd1a645","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":20,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563807451","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-62f54a76a335e895209ba8083959748a_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546280660,"updated_time":1546280660,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":28,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"nobody","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"前几天那般傲慢的态度，莫非全知乎人都忘了？如此信誓旦旦说自己证明了哥猜，哪怕是各路大V拿事实说话也始终不接受，直到今晚这个覆水难收的局面\u003cbr\u003e其实在他发出他那篇荒谬的证明之前他还有机会挽回自己颜面，但是现在没有任何机会了，前几天已经有很多人提醒过他小心网络暴力，如果是错的趁早承认，你见过他有这么做吗？隔一段时间来个倒计时，若真证明何必如此吊众人胃口？以此手段来博取眼球，不就是他的目的吗？现在又开始洗了\u003cbr\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg data-rawwidth=\"1242\" data-rawheight=\"2208\" src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-62f54a76a335e895209ba8083959748a_b.png\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1242\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-62f54a76a335e895209ba8083959748a_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg data-rawwidth=\"1242\" data-rawheight=\"2208\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1242'%20height='2208'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1242\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-62f54a76a335e895209ba8083959748a_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-62f54a76a335e895209ba8083959748a_b.png\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cbr\u003e你只是一个高中生，几个月前还在纠结洛必达法则和四面体的面积求和，离真正的数学还差着十万八千里，却到处宣扬着能证明哥猜。无知，还不自知。要明白放在知乎这个网络平台上会是什么影响，不考虑后果就行动，而且有无数次认识到自己错误的机会却一个都没把握住，那就真的别怪网友了，自己作死怪不得别人。\u003cbr\u003e无语了，那些真正为数学奉献毕生精力的大师们得不到流量和关注，一个认真作答写文章的数学大V经营几年，关注量还不如一个哗众取宠的高中生用一周时间不到获取的数目，这是何等的讽刺呢？你们现在的关心鼓励和宽容，置前人和真正有实力的人于何地呢？让他们有何感想？","editable_content":"","excerpt":"前几天那般傲慢的态度，莫非全知乎人都忘了？如此信誓旦旦说自己证明了哥猜，哪怕是各路大V拿事实说话也始终不接受，直到今晚这个覆水难收的局面 其实在他发出他那篇荒谬的证明之前他还有机会挽回自己颜面，但是现在没有任何机会了，前几天已经有很多人提醒…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%